commit.message:
emit-rtl.c (try_split): Do not abort on non-INSN_P.

2002-06-11  David S. Miller  <davem@redhat.com>

	* emit-rtl.c (try_split): Do not abort on non-INSN_P.
	Only run RTX equality checks on INSN_P rtl.
